songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
You want me, but he needs you
Yet you're tellin' me that everything's cool
Tryin' to convince me, to do as you say
Just go along and see things your way

[Verse 2]
And keep it on that XO (Oh baby)
Nobody has to know, has to know
Not your momma, not your sister, not your daddy
Just keep it on that XO (Yeah-ah-ah)
Nobody has to know, has to know, has to know, oh
songs.title: Keep it on that XO (Interlude)
